cdata.name: Cloud
cdata.desc:
Cloudwithme is a platform that provides hosting solutions for cloud services. Cloudwithmewill leverage the Ethereum blockchain to provide a decentralized cloud services ecosystem. Taking advantage of a peer-to-peernetwork to manage the hosting of cloud services and smart contract's features.

The Cloud token (CLD) is an ERC-20 token that will beused to distribute pro-rata payments to the Crowd Cloud providers.
